<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center">NSW PS2 Moduli</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">NSW PS2 Moduli bilan Klaviatura va Sichqoncha Boshqaruvi</p>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Umumiy Ma'lumot</h2>
        <p>NSW PS2 Moduli PS/2 interfeysidan foydalanib klaviatura va sichqoncha signalini qabul qilish uchun mo'ljallangan. Bu modul robototexnika, avtomatlashtirish tizimlari va boshqa turli xil loyihalarda keng qo'llanilishi mumkin. U Arduino va boshqa mikrokontrollerlar bilan mos keladi.</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_ps2.jpg" alt="NSW PS2 Moduli" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Asosiy Xususiyatlari</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Ishlash kuchlanishi: 3.3V-5V DC</li>
            <li>PS/2 interfeysi</li>
            <li>Modul hajmi: 30 x 20 x 10 mm</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Ilovalar</h2>
        <p>NSW PS2 Moduli quyidagi turli loyihalarda ishlatilishi mumkin:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Robototexnika</li>
            <li>Avtomatlashtirish Tizimlari</li>
            <li>Klaviatura va sichqoncha interfeysi</li>
            <li>DIY Gadjetlar</li>
            <li>Ta'lim Loyiha</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Pin Tafsilotlari</h2>
        <p>NSW PS2 Moduli portida quyidagi pinlar mavjud:</p>
        <table class="table table-bordered">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Pin</th>
                    <th>Vazifasi</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>GND</td>
                    <td>Manfiy to'k</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>VCC</td>
                    <td>Quvvatlantirish manbai</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>DATA</td>
                    <td>PS/2 ma'lumot liniyasi</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>CLK</td>
                    <td>PS/2 soat liniyasi</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Simlarni Ulash Rejimi</h2>
        <p>● RJ25 bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>NSW PS2 Moduli RJ25 porti orqali ulanishi mumkin. Makeblock Orion-da RJ25 portidan foydalanganda, uni mos keluvchi portga ulashingiz kerak:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_ps2_rj25.jpg" alt="NSW PS2 RJ25 Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">

        <p>● Dupont simi bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>Dupont simidan modulni Arduino UNO asos paneliga ulash uchun foydalanilganda, uning DATA va CLK pinlarini Arduino digital pinlariga quyidagicha ulash lozim:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_ps2_dupont.jpg" alt="NSW PS2 Dupont Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Dasturlash Bo'yicha Qo'llanma</h2>
        <p>Arduino Dasturlash</p>
        <p>Agar dastur yozish uchun Arduino dan foydalansangiz, NSW PS2 Modulini boshqarish uchun quyidagi koddan foydalanishingiz mumkin:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-cpp">
// Arduino dastur kodi
#include &lt;PS2Keyboard.h>

const int DataPin = 8;
const int IRQpin = 3;
PS2Keyboard keyboard;

void setup() {
    Serial.begin(9600);
    keyboard.begin(DataPin, IRQpin);
    Serial.println("PS2 klaviatura ishga tushirildi.");
}

void loop() {
    if (keyboard.available()) {
        char c = keyboard.read();
        Serial.print(c);
    }
}
        </code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h3>Prinsipiy Tahlil</h3>
        <p>NSW PS2 Moduli PS/2 interfeysidan foydalanib klaviatura va sichqoncha signalini qabul qilish uchun mo'ljallangan. Bu modulning asosiy funktsiyasi robototexnika va avtomatlashtirish tizimlarida klaviatura va sichqoncha boshqaruvini amalga oshirishdir. DATA va CLK pinlari orqali ma'lumot uzatish va qabul qilish amalga oshiriladi.</p>
    </div>

